<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="101" type="distribution">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="101">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
Greece: Thrace, southernmost foothills of the Rhodope (Ροδόπη) Mountains. (Fig. 7), the regional units of Rhodope and 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Xánthi">Xanthi</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="8" pageNumber="101" type="name derivation">
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="101">Name derivation.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="8" pageNumber="101">
Patronymic, named in honour of our longtime friend, entomologist Jan Schneider (Praha, Czech Republic), an excellent 
<taxonomicName family="Geotrupidae" lsidName="" pageId="8" pageNumber="101" rank="family">Geotrupidae</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName family="Silphidae" lsidName="" pageId="8" pageNumber="101" rank="family">Silphidae</taxonomicName>
specialist.
</paragraph>
